          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "What is Barzel Scripture Intelligence?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "Barzel Scripture Intelligence is a Bible MCP server that gives AI clients 54 tools for Scripture search, verse lookup, passage analysis, cross-references, Christian theology, original-language study, sermon preparation, teaching, and devotionals."
